18:52.107 --> 18:56.674
had three children. And then I went to work in the 
courthouse, the tax collector. And then when the

19:04.886 --> 19:08.451
war came along, I worked. I was chief clerk of the 
draft board for five years. And then after the war

19:12.497 --> 19:21.270
was over, but before the end of the draft office, I 
quit and went back to the tax collector's office.

19:22.550 --> 19:28.397
Okay, what changes did you notice, like, during 
the war when, like, most of the men were away? Did

19:29.538 --> 19:43.074
this community become more dependent on the, for 
instance, like the women, did they take over the

19:29.538 --> 19:43.074
stores and most of the businesses, or did, you 
know, like, was it just most of the young men that

