25:43.218 --> 25:52.149
at the other station. They hadn't opened up. These 
guys had a modulated Ford truck, stake bed on it,

25:54.944 --> 26:01.351
tarp on it. Well, I knew who it was. Running 
whiskey, bringing whiskey from down there in the

26:07.138 --> 26:11.262
bottom going to Houston.

