27:51.972 --> 28:00.880
cedar house. Come back here at noon, I saw them 
dollar and a half store in the

28:00.900 --> 28:09.869
truck. You know, I didn't know about that. I'm 
learning things. Some of their customers, some of

28:13.332 --> 28:20.019
their customers somewhere down the line, I 
